biotools.summary: A complete network for ascorbic acid (including associated pathways) with a list of the identified genetic variants in tomato genome through a methodology that integrates gene annotations and transcriptome. It represents the only available collection, exhaustive and detailed, on ascorbic acid network in tomato.
